<title>UK: Sanderson Electronics appoints fin director.</title>
<headline>Sanderson Electronics appoints fin director.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1996-10-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Sanderson Electronics Plc said on Tuesday it had appointed Roger Pawson, 52, group finance director.</p>
<p>The responsibility for the company's financial matters used to be handled by chairman Paul Thompson.</p>
<p>Sanderson Electronics said the company's growth had prompted it to create the finance director post.</p>
<p>Pawson joined Sanderson as a non-executive director in 1994, having been finance director at Provident Financial Plc before.</p>
